newsitem.title: USA: Most IMM currencies end higher in moderate trading.
newsitem.headline: Most IMM currencies end higher in moderate trading.

text.p: Aug 23 - Most IMM currency futures finsihed higher in moderate trading. September yen finished higher in a reverse from early weakness, drifting up with strength in marks and Swiss. A U.S. bank bought 1,500 Sept yen on the close, traders said. Traders said yen players nervous heading into heavy Japanese data line-up next week.
